wikipedia_page.main: Commander John Tapling Fremantle, 5th Baron Cottesloe, 6th Baron Fremantle,  (22 January 1927 – 21 May 2018) was a British baron in the Peerage of the United Kingdom.

response: The Betsey Wynne public house and restaurant in Swanbourne, Buckinghamshire, was built in 2006 by the Fremantle Trust, a body run by Thomas Henry Fremantle and his father John Fremantle, 5th Baron Cottesloe.
* John Fremantle, 5th Baron Cottesloe (b. 1927), Commander of the Royal Navy
